Brownfield land

View the data

Explore the brownfield land data on this page, which has been collected and processed by the Digital Land pipeline.

URL of the register:
https://files.datapress.com/leeds/dataset/bradford-brownfield-register/2017-12-12T13:17:30.67/Bradford_brownfieldregister_2017-12-01_rev1.csv
Published 22 May 2018
Last collected on 30 July 2018
From:
City of Bradford Metropolitan District Council

How we've processed this data

The Digital Land pipeline collects the data and fixes common errors that do not align with the data standard.

Related content

  • Brownfield land data standard
  • Brownfield land register regulations (2017)

Facts from the data

The following information has been extracted from the register.

The register references 1 organisation.

It reports 216 brownfield sites. 0 of these have an end date and are no longer considered brownfield land.

Not including sites with an end date, there are:

  • 181.94 hectares of brownfield land
  • between 8835 and 10367 potential dwellings that could be built
  • 0 sites have permission in principle
